The paper deals with influence propagation in social networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of social and information networks (cs.SI) and social and economic systems (cs.SOC). The paper also proposes new optimization problems and algorithms, which are related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
